              Future Design Factory is a passion-driven learning hub at <strong>NHL Stenden University of Applied
              Science</strong> open to national and international students, teachers, researchers, and businesses.
              Operating under the umbrella of CMD and part of the School of Design, we create Futures
              Visions for a better everyday life and design sustainable new solutions for people and the
              planet. In collaboration with various academies, we are building a multidisciplinary learning
              culture through the application of our Future Thinking theory combined with Design Based
              Education.
            </p>
