            <p>
              RUN-EU amplifies the vision by equipping students, researchers, and academics with green,
              digital, and inclusive skills to support sustainable economic, social, cultural, and environmental
              growth in Europe. Focused on bridging regional development gaps, the network empowers
              stakeholders to enhance competitiveness and resilience across the EU. By 2030, RUN-EU aims
              to establish itself as a fully integrated European University, creating a groundbreaking European
              Zone for Interregional Development through an innovative, multinational alliance model.
